{
    "name": "Outlaw Troop",
    "type": "monster",
    "sections": [
        {
            "name": "Ecology",
            "type": "section",
            "html": "<b>Environment</b> any land<br/><b>Organization</b> solitary or band (2\u20134)<br/><b>Treasure</b> standard"
        },
        {
            "name": "Special Abilities",
            "type": "section",
            "html": "<b>Protect Ally (Ex)</b> The troop provides soft cover to allies sharing its space. Such allies treat squares occupied by the troop as difficult terrain, must succeed at a concentration check (DC = 15 + spell level) to cast spells while so protected, and don\u2019t take troop damage from being within the troop\u2019s space"
        },
        {
            "name": "Description",
            "type": "section",
            "html": "While individually not much of a threat, these low-level fighters turn into a serious menace to travelers on remote roads when they work together as a troop."
        }
    ],
    "html": "<i>Over two dozen men and women clad in chain shirts and leather armor brandish their knives and swords menacingly.</i>",
